{"title":"python virtualenvironment 迁移","date":"2019-12-03T14:30:49.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Dec 3, 2019","L":"12/03/2019","MM-DD":"12-03"},"link":"2019/12/03/Python/python-virtualenvironment-迁移","tags":["tips"],"categories":["Python"],"updated":"2020-11-19T07:36:17.967Z","content":"<h1 id=\"python-virtualenvironment-迁移\">python virtualenvironment 迁移<a href=\"2019/12/03/Python/python-virtualenvironment-迁移#python-virtualenvironment-迁移\"></a></h1><p>python virtualenvironment的便利之处就在于构建了独立的python运行环境，工程所需要的环境可以很方便地打包随程序迁移到其他路径/其他机器上。</p>\n<p>最开始以为python虚拟环境直接跟随工程打包起来，到其他机器就可以用了，真的是too young too naive…然后就收到报错啦。</p>\n<p>python虚拟环境迁移的正确打开方式是：</p>\n<h2 id=\"方法1\">方法1<a href=\"2019/12/03/Python/python-virtualenvironment-迁移#方法1\"></a></h2><p>在移动工程后，修改虚拟环境中的路径，如active, pip, ipython等等</p>\n<p>如activate.bat下：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">set</span> &quot;VIRTUAL_ENV=C:\\Users\\admin\\PycharmProjects\\venv_test\\venv&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>但是这个方法有些麻烦，所以还是推荐选择方法2</p>\n<h2 id=\"方法2\">方法2<a href=\"2019/12/03/Python/python-virtualenvironment-迁移#方法2\"></a></h2><p>在原本路径的venv1中执行<code>pip freeze &gt; requirements.txt</code>将包依赖的信息保存在requirements.txt文件中。</p>\n<p>到新路径下的venv2中执行<code>pip install -r requirements.txt</code>，pip就会自动从网上下载并安装所有包。</p>\n<p>当然还有其他的方法…</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>若有误或待改进之处，望前辈们指正！</p>\n<p>转载请注明出处！</p>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"Python基础","link":"2019/12/08/Python/Python基础"},"next":{"title":"与各种龟速对抗","link":"2019/11/24/其他/与各种龟速对抗"},"plink":"http://ciel07yxh.top/2019/12/03/Python/python-virtualenvironment-迁移/","toc":[{"title":"python virtualenvironment 迁移","id":"python-virtualenvironment-迁移","index":"1","children":[{"title":"方法1","id":"方法1","index":"1.1"},{"title":"方法2","id":"方法2","index":"1.2"}]}]}